description:
What will you do when you dont have access to healthcare? Are you prepping for dealing with health problems yourself at home during the time of no buy no sell, when help is not on the way? This presentation looks at proactive measures to prevent the most common health problems we have today and home remedies you can use to treat common, acute health crises at home. Learn the top 10 medical issues that send patients to the doctors office and survivalist medicine for treating them. Specific remedies for treating upper respiratory illnesses are considered in this first part.
